{"tid":1215612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遭市民質疑鄭松泰勇武去咗邊 鄭松泰助理：好似你地咁咩，攞盡光環！","createTime":"2019-06-13T07:42:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T08:35:03.000Z","uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ebb494a4e619a6730e60a59e9f4517c79f503331","tid":1215612,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:42:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/562212700/posts/10156661141317701?s=753094347&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F562212700%2Fposts%2F10156661141317701%3Fs%3D753094347%26sfns%3Dmo&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWNLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=c801f7c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/562212700/posts/10156661141317701?s=753094347&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n琴晚凌晨同朋友路過金鐘道嘅時候見到 Chung-Tai Cheng 鄭松泰議員同佢嘅唔知走狗定助理，朋友只係問左句：「鄭生今日勇武去左邊度？」。隔離果位唔知助理定走狗竟然話：「好似你地咁咩，今日攞盡光環。」<br />\n聽到真係 #當堂嚇一跳然後得啖笑<br />\n下？我地wor？我地班廢青點解要攞光環<br />\n對我地呢d普羅大眾黎講冇意義架wor<br />\n再者攞光環點及你班議員啊 我地只係選民之嘛<br />\n拍馬都追唔上啦😇<br />\n#唔係親眼目睹都唔敢相信熱狗咁樣公然挑選民機<br />\n#好彩我當年新西冇投俾你<br />\n#鄭松泰 #熱血公民 #反送中 #612野餐"},{"pid":"cdcf9dda1bbaf84901b2d9d2f203d9512f056c64","tid":1215612,"uid":199048,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:46:16.000Z","msg":"得字，圖都冇張，<br />\n講見到佢打示威者都得。"},{"pid":"7474e6df3d2ca148709e21b4660af7f559f677ed","tid":1215612,"uid":18569,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:46:47.000Z","msg":"每個月份糧咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鬼同你勇武咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbeff04150b9568daf259690839cd98d6347896c","tid":1215612,"uid":28114,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:47:07.000Z","msg":"連鄺囝都勇過呢條人型垃圾十倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c478c3297196f90bd284c1949aa8ea9046713567","tid":1215612,"uid":165450,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply